## 8. Edge Cases & Failure Handling

| Scenario                                           | Detection                                                           | Recovery                                                                                                    |
| -------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Phone leaves mid-recording                         | WebSocket `close` event from phone                                  | Show warning; recording on phone continues locally (WS reconnects on upload)                                |
| rAF jitter > 2ms                                   | Optional diagnostics on Sync Marker mount                            | Warn user; jitter is not a timing input but may indicate an unstable display environment                    |
| Sync Marker tab backgrounded                       | `visibilitychange` event                                             | Pause marker; show "Recording paused — please keep this tab visible"                                        |
| User clicks > 3 seeds                              | Seed count check in BallSeedPicker                                  | Toast: "Maximum 3 balls"; refuse 4th click                                                                  |
| Frame PNG 404 (ffmpeg incomplete)                  | `img.onerror`                                                       | Show grey placeholder; poll once per second until available                                                 |
| Upload blob > 2GB                                  | `blob.size` check before XHR                                        | Chunk upload using XHR with Range headers (Node must support) OR warn user to reduce recording duration     |
| calibration:complete with reprojection_error > 1px | Result inspection in calibrationStore                               | Show red warning: "Poor calibration quality (Xpx). Results may be inaccurate. Retry or use ruler fallback." |
| No phones connected, only PC webcam                | `sessionStore.cameras.filter(c => c.type === 'phone').length === 0` | Allow single-camera mode; no QR code required                                                               |
| Correction on already-corrected frame              | `isCorrected` flag check                                            | Allow; replace previous correction; re-propagate                                                            |
| Track data partially missing on page reload        | GET /api/experiments/:id → check `results/tracks.json` exists       | Re-fetch from Node file API; restore to trackingStore                                                       |

